==製作==
自2007年以來，《[[黑塔|黑塔]]》不斷傳出改編的消息，但仍都沒有實際作為。[[J·J·亞柏拉罕|J·J·亞柏拉罕]]（2007年至2009年）和[[朗·霍華|朗·霍華]]（2010年至2015年）都曾計劃擔任導演，最後由確定[[尼科萊·阿爾賽|尼科萊·阿爾賽]]執導，而霍華則擔任監製。

===拍攝===
電影正式於2016年4月在[[南非|南非]]拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pesce|first1=Nicole Lyn|title=‘The Dark Tower’: First look at Idris Elba as the Gunslinger|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/dark-tower-idris-elba-gunslinger-article-1.2639947|accessdate=2016-06-28|work=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|date=2016-05-17|archive-date=2017-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801234502/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/dark-tower-idris-elba-gunslinger-article-1.2639947|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而劇組也會在[[紐約|紐約]]取景<ref>{{cite news|title=Man in black! Matthew McConaughey dyes hair darker for his role|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3668873/Man-black-Matthew-McConaughey-gets-character-shows-freshly-dyed-hair-set-Dark-Tower.html|accessdate=2016-07-01|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|date=2016-06-30|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160715064827/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3668873/Man-black-Matthew-McConaughey-gets-character-shows-freshly-dyed-hair-set-Dark-Tower.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年10月，電影試映後，索尼和MRC又花了600萬美元進行部分重拍。

==發行==
電影原本定於2017年2月17日在美國上映，但因後製未能趕上而延期至2017年7月28日。2017年4月初，《黑塔》的上映日延期至2017年8月4日，因索尼將該片與《[[表情符號電影|表情符號電影]]》的上映日互換。

===市場營銷===
首支預告片定於2016年下半年的某節日釋出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/dark-tower-movie-trailer-release-christmas/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2016-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110054646/http://screenrant.com/dark-tower-movie-trailer-release-christmas/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但於2016年10月10日時，一支粗剪版的預告洩露於網上，之後該預告隨即被移除<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://io9.gizmodo.com/the-leaked-dark-tower-trailer-has-a-lot-of-modern-day-n-1787626050 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-11-04 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011131457/http://io9.gizmodo.com/the-leaked-dark-tower-trailer-has-a-lot-of-modern-day-n-1787626050 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==回響==
===評價===
《黑塔》獲得多數負面的評論，主要批評電影將金的原作簡化，而使劇情枯燥無味，但艾巴和麥康納的演出則獲得了讚賞<ref name=reviews>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/the-dark-tower-reviews-critics-release-date-trailer-stephen-king-adaptation-idris-elba-matthew-a7874286.html|title=The Dark Tower review round-up: Stephen King adaptation disappoints both newbies and fans|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=2017-08-03|accessdate=2017-08-10|archive-date=2017-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014234041/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/the-dark-tower-reviews-critics-release-date-trailer-stephen-king-adaptation-idris-elba-matthew-a7874286.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=reviews2>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2017/08/03/the-dark-tower-review-round-up/|title=Sorry, Stephen King. Critics hated 'The Dark Tower'|work=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|date=2017-08-03|accessdate=2017-08-08|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809090329/http://mashable.com/2017/08/03/the-dark-tower-review-round-up/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]基於126條評論，僅持有18%的新鮮度，平均等級為4.1 / 10<ref>{{cite web|title=''The Dark Tower'' (2017)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_dark_tower_2017|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango]]|accessdate=2017-08-07|archive-date=2017-03-26|archive-url=https://archive.is/20170326154531/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/atomic_blonde_2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分34，口碑不佳<ref>{{cite web |title=''The Dark Tower'' reviews |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-tower |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2017-08-08 |archive-date=2017-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828215332/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-dark-tower |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F間落在「B」<ref name=opening />。

===票房===
在北美，《黑塔》與《{{link-en|綁架 (2017年電影)|Kidnap (2017 film)|綁架}}》、《[[底特律_(電影)|底特律]]》共同上映競爭，《黑塔》估計於首週能從3451間戲院中獲得2000萬美元的票房<ref name=preview>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-dark-tower-20170802-htmlstory.html|title=Sony's long-awaited 'Dark Tower' may unseat 'Dunkirk' with $25-million box-office premiere|website=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2017-08-02|accessdate=2017-08-07|archive-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807160354/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/la-fi-ct-movie-projector-dark-tower-20170802-htmlstory.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它於週四晚間獲得了180萬美元，並於第一天獲得770萬美元的票房。美國首映週末票房收入為1950萬美元，位居當週票房冠軍<ref name=opening>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/the-dark-tower-detroit-kidnap-dunkirk-weekend-box-office-opening-1202142448/|title=‘The Dark Tower’ Opens To $18M+ In Diverse Marketplace: Was The Decade-Plus Battle To The Screen Worth It?|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2017-08-05|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804173240/http://deadline.com/2017/08/the-dark-tower-detroit-kidnap-dunkirk-weekend-box-office-opening-1202142448/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

